1
00:00:03,230 --> 00:00:04,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoya.</font>

2
00:00:05,570 --> 00:00:06,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi!</font>

3
00:00:16,910 --> 00:00:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've finally caught you, 
my bird in a cage.</font>

4
00:00:21,250 --> 00:00:26,260
<font size="20"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><b><font size="16">{\an7}A Diva in the Cage</font></b></font></font>

5
00:00:50,830 --> 00:00:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will continue to sing 
the song of hope right here.</font>

6
00:00:57,570 --> 00:01:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until the universe is no more.</font>

7
00:01:07,460 --> 00:01:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}A calling arises from deep 
within in my burning heart</i></font>

8
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:14,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's Show Time</i></font>

9
00:01:23,230 --> 00:01:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The price of living in the time of freedom</i></font>

10
00:01:26,220 --> 00:01:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}"So, what do you want to do?"</i></font>

11
00:01:27,830 --> 00:01:33,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just standing there with my empty body</i></font>

12
00:01:33,470 --> 00:01:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Like a calling to protect the world</i></font>

13
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:44,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I craved an unequaled gift</i></font>

14
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Lost in night's darkness</i></font>

15
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:51,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Until a voice called out to me</i></font>

16
00:01:51,190 --> 00:01:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Like the light that declares the dawn</i></font>

17
00:01:55,310 --> 00:02:00,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'll take you with me at 
any cost (I pray and wish)</i></font>

18
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:02,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Beyond the Echo-verse (To the future)</i></font>

19
00:02:01,550 --> 00:02:04,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just being with you makes me strong</i></font>

20
00:02:04,310 --> 00:02:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's not an exaggeration</i></font>

21
00:02:05,690 --> 00:02:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}That encounter was a supernova 
(Our eyes were locked)</i></font>

22
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In an instant, everything that I am 
(In an instant)</i></font>

23
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Will be changed forever (Just to be)</i></font>

24
00:02:15,620 --> 00:02:19,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A calling arises from deep
 within in my burning heart</i></font>

25
00:02:19,460 --> 00:02:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Destiny is Calling us now</i></font>

26
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just to be who we are</i></font>

27
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Destiny is Calling us now</i></font>

28
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:29,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just to be by your side</i></font>

29
00:02:41,350 --> 00:02:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck is that?!</font>

30
00:02:42,460 --> 00:02:43,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So huge!</font>

31
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kokytos.</font>

32
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know what it is, Medea?</font>

33
00:02:47,850 --> 00:02:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have seen it activated once before.</font>

34
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:54,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ten years ago.</font>

35
00:02:54,990 --> 00:02:57,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ten years ago. You mean...</font>

36
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:04,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It finally awakens once more.</font>

37
00:03:05,190 --> 00:03:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kokytos, which went to sleep 
along with Lady Eden ten years ago.</font>

38
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:18,760
<font size="20"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="16">Ten Years Ago</font></b></font></font>

39
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:26,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Earth.</font>

40
00:03:26,070 --> 00:03:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's where he is.</font>

41
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you get us there, Priest?</font>

42
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:34,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is going to solve everything, right?</font>

43
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our planet, our people... and most
importantly, Lady Eden will be saved?</font>

44
00:03:40,870 --> 00:03:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we can get all of Earth's
 Idea, it is possible!</font>

45
00:03:44,810 --> 00:03:50,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moreover, he betrayed us and 
contacted the earthlings.</font>

46
00:03:50,740 --> 00:03:54,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They must be annihilated now
or it will come back and bite us.</font>

47
00:03:56,010 --> 00:03:59,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saving our planet or defeating Orphe.</font>

48
00:03:59,570 --> 00:04:02,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which do you wish to achieve?</font>

49
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does it matter?</font>

50
00:04:07,420 --> 00:04:10,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Regardless of the purpose, 
the action we must take is the same!</font>

51
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:15,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Release the Mirage, and take everything 
from Earth with the power of the Diva!</font>

52
00:04:18,380 --> 00:04:20,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please forgive me, Lady Eden.</font>

53
00:04:23,460 --> 00:04:30,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must borrow your power 
one last time so I can save you.</font>

54
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:37,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Using the power of the Diva 
to control the Mirage?</font>

55
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:41,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By being in close proximity to Earth,</font>

56
00:04:41,340 --> 00:04:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the location and range of the Mirage 
can be easily controlled.</font>

57
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:47,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was meant to be the ultimate weapon.</font>

58
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you kidding me?</font>

59
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is he using a bastard cheat move now?</font>

60
00:04:52,460 --> 00:04:55,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there a reason why it 
wasn't used for ten years?</font>

61
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are two reasons.</font>

62
00:04:58,670 --> 00:05:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The new Diva; Lady Nagi's power
reduced its might to a minimum.</font>

63
00:05:05,990 --> 00:05:11,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And its last use has put 
Lady Eden, our former Diva,</font>

64
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:14,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">into an eternal slumber.</font>

65
00:05:14,230 --> 00:05:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Then why is it activated now?</font>

66
00:05:17,180 --> 00:05:19,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Diva of XENOS 
is asleep now, isn't she?</font>

67
00:05:19,310 --> 00:05:20,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then how...?</font>

68
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:34,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It follows that it is the new Diva 
who's powering Kokytos.</font>

69
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:39,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Priest. No, Lord Archon.</font>

70
00:05:40,170 --> 00:05:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time for sure, we shall
take Earth with Kokytos.</font>

71
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is not Lady Eden you need to face now.</font>

72
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:54,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What you must do is to bind the new Diva.</font>

73
00:05:55,330 --> 00:06:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give the Idea of Earth to this bird in 
a cage and make her sing for our planet.</font>

74
00:06:03,050 --> 00:06:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what happens to Lady Eden?</font>

75
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will she continue to sleep 
as she has been?</font>

76
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But our planet will come back!</font>

77
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our people will awaken!</font>

78
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Idea of the Earth 
and the blessings of the Diva</font>

79
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:22,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will give us XENOS 
the power to regenerate!</font>

80
00:06:24,170 --> 00:06:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Idea of the Earth 
and the blessings of the Diva.</font>

81
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:34,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that power, the blessings 
of the new Diva,</font>

82
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are given only to Lady Eden, 
then perchance...</font>

83
00:06:39,660 --> 00:06:41,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you thinking, Archo—</font>

84
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Archon, you bastard!</font>

85
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:55,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not only Samael, but you're 
sacrificing yourself to Kokytos?!</font>

86
00:06:56,450 --> 00:06:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not a sacrifice for Kokytos.</font>

87
00:07:00,020 --> 00:07:03,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nourishment for Lady Eden!</font>

88
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:08,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Eden has reached the end of her life!</font>

89
00:07:08,470 --> 00:07:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why can't you see that, Archon?!</font>

90
00:07:11,130 --> 00:07:16,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't seriously suggest that you're 
willing to dedicate XENOS's everything</font>

91
00:07:16,770 --> 00:07:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to a single individual who 
will never wake up again?!</font>

92
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I should have done 
from the beginning!</font>

93
00:07:23,540 --> 00:07:29,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When Lady Eden's power started to 
weaken several hundred years ago.</font>

94
00:07:29,970 --> 00:07:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I should have done!</font>

95
00:07:33,860 --> 00:07:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I created her for this day.</font>

96
00:07:37,730 --> 00:07:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From the DNA of Lady Eden and myself.</font>

97
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:46,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that Lady Eden's life 
can be saved, nothing else!</font>

98
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:55,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are you saying that the new Diva 
is you and Lady Eden's...?</i></font>

99
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:01,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Orphe was right.</i></font>

100
00:08:02,610 --> 00:08:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He never betrayed us.</i></font>

101
00:08:09,860 --> 00:08:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right, Apollo.</font>

102
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:19,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That guy, Orphe, never doubted anyone.</font>

103
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since that day, you two parting ways...</font>

104
00:08:27,050 --> 00:08:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and XENOS and the earthlings 
killing each other...</font>

105
00:08:33,620 --> 00:08:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was predetermined to happen.</font>

106
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:42,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I did that to Orphe.</i></font>

107
00:08:45,570 --> 00:08:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you know, Apollo.</font>

108
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:51,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was you who gave Archon the final push.</font>

109
00:08:52,830 --> 00:08:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ten years ago, out of hatred for Orphe,</font>

110
00:08:56,820 --> 00:09:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you activated the incomplete Kokytos 
and consigned Eden to eternal sleep.</font>

111
00:09:04,470 --> 00:09:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ever since then, 
Archon's purpose has changed.</font>

112
00:09:09,590 --> 00:09:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He decided to save one and only one 
out of tens of billions of XENOS.</font>

113
00:09:16,630 --> 00:09:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We became part of the sacrifice 
to revive Eden.</font>

114
00:09:22,290 --> 00:09:25,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you knew that, then why did you...?</font>

115
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:31,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, nothing he'll do 
will ever resurrect Eden.</font>

116
00:09:31,550 --> 00:09:36,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, the true destruction 
of all will come as I hoped.</font>

117
00:09:36,830 --> 00:09:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not just the destruction of Earth 
and XENOS, but the whole universe.</font>

118
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:56,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let go. Let go of me!</font>

119
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where am I?</font>

120
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's finally mine.</font>

121
00:10:14,290 --> 00:10:16,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Archon...san?</font>

122
00:10:16,950 --> 00:10:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Copy of Lady Eden.</font>

123
00:10:19,490 --> 00:10:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And our dear daughter.</font>

124
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

125
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will now absorb the Idea 
of the whole universe.</font>

126
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:37,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And give it all to Lady Eden.</font>

127
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why am I doing that?</font>

128
00:10:42,220 --> 00:10:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So my beloved lady can live on forever.</font>

129
00:10:48,710 --> 00:10:54,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you'll destroy everyone 
and everything except for Eden-san?</font>

130
00:10:54,910 --> 00:10:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think Eden-san...</font>

131
00:10:57,950 --> 00:11:01,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the person you love... 
will be happy to see that?</font>

132
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:05,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think she can smile 
from the bottom of her heart?</font>

133
00:11:08,190 --> 00:11:14,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will have to ask her once she wakes up.</font>

134
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take that!</font>

135
00:11:27,820 --> 00:11:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really is here, Medea-san!</font>

136
00:11:30,860 --> 00:11:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Move up already.</font>

137
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're waiting down here.</font>

138
00:11:33,780 --> 00:11:37,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, Jeez! There's no end to this!</font>

139
00:11:37,070 --> 00:11:38,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's use this spacecraft!</font>

140
00:11:47,190 --> 00:11:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going to go after Nagi?</font>

141
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I am!</font>

142
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Kyoya-kun, we're totally 
surrounded on all sides.</font>

143
00:11:56,530 --> 00:11:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think so?</font>

144
00:11:59,020 --> 00:12:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi... Our center was taken away again.</font>

145
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:06,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the same situation it was
before we got here, that's all.</font>

146
00:12:07,190 --> 00:12:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The people on Earth 
are consumed by anger.</font>

147
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't have a live concert 
like we used to—</font>

148
00:12:12,370 --> 00:12:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be fine.</font>

149
00:12:13,420 --> 00:12:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they hear our songs up close, 
I know they'll regain their good hearts.</font>

150
00:12:18,590 --> 00:12:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa?!</font>

151
00:12:21,300 --> 00:12:22,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow...</font>

152
00:12:23,290 --> 00:12:26,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like you really 
haven't given up yet.</font>

153
00:12:26,610 --> 00:12:27,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

154
00:12:27,270 --> 00:12:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you were going to whine,
I was going to take over as leader.</font>

155
00:12:32,020 --> 00:12:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

156
00:12:32,810 --> 00:12:34,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you tested me!</font>

157
00:12:34,530 --> 00:12:36,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would I believe you?</font>

158
00:12:36,940 --> 00:12:39,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I had faith in you, Kyoya-kun.</font>

159
00:12:39,950 --> 00:12:40,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I smell a lie!</font>

160
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For being in a hurry, 
you all seem very relaxed.</font>

161
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's totally egging us on!</font>

162
00:12:49,410 --> 00:12:52,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're pretty lax yourself, you know?</font>

163
00:12:52,940 --> 00:12:56,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Medea-san has assimilated 
as a member of Harmonia.</font>

164
00:13:00,010 --> 00:13:03,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi, I will follow you 
to the end of the world.</font>

165
00:13:04,740 --> 00:13:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She could've smiled 
from the bottom of her heart</font>

166
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if only you'd told her that 
on daily basis.</font>

167
00:13:09,880 --> 00:13:11,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa?!</font>

168
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:15,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

169
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:19,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have the happiest 
ending with a smile.</font>

170
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:20,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With Siren, of course!</font>

171
00:13:24,620 --> 00:13:32,370
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="13"><font color="#771230">{\an8}This is Nagi's masterpiece!



Write some awesome music for it!</font></font></b></font></font>

172
00:13:25,630 --> 00:13:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're SI-VIS's Diva.</font>

173
00:13:27,670 --> 00:13:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, their former Diva, correct?</font>

174
00:13:32,370 --> 00:13:36,550
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="13"><font color="#5e574c">Team Formation for
the Next Concert</font></font></font></font>

175
00:13:32,370 --> 00:13:36,550
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="13"><font color="#5e574c">Center!</font></font></font></font>

176
00:13:32,370 --> 00:13:36,550
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="13"><font color="#5e574c">Soji</font></font></font></font>

177
00:13:32,370 --> 00:13:36,550
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="13"><font color="#5e574c">Kyoya</font></font></font></font>

178
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are... a friend of June. Yeah?</font>

179
00:13:39,220 --> 00:13:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A friend of June. 
That's what you choose to call me.</font>

180
00:13:45,380 --> 00:13:47,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not the sworn enemy of the world?</font>

181
00:13:52,790 --> 00:13:57,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, I'm not a <i>former</i> Diva.</font>

182
00:13:57,820 --> 00:14:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still the main vocalist of SI-VIS.</font>

183
00:14:01,470 --> 00:14:03,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you find us?</font>

184
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">June told me.</font>

185
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He wanted me to save his friend.</font>

186
00:14:08,300 --> 00:14:11,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He disclosed such confidential 
information to an archenemy like me.</font>

187
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's absolutely irrational.</font>

188
00:14:13,980 --> 00:14:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I heard you also gave every weapon
you had to Asukai-kun.</font>

189
00:14:18,980 --> 00:14:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you being irrational as well?</font>

190
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:36,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And? You came all the way here 
to see if I'm doing okay?</font>

191
00:14:36,730 --> 00:14:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, and I knew it at a glance.</font>

192
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can no longer sing.</font>

193
00:14:43,060 --> 00:14:49,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every time you try to sing or play, 
Lukos' curse sucks Idea from you.</font>

194
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:53,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And eventually, your presence 
will not be recognized by others.</font>

195
00:14:53,770 --> 00:14:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention, one strum of the guitar 
must be causing you unbearable pain.</font>

196
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:09,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I'm more present in this world 
than Nagi was a year ago.</font>

197
00:15:10,180 --> 00:15:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, not even one percent of her 
was present in this world.</font>

198
00:15:15,740 --> 00:15:20,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was translucent, quiet, and so floaty.</font>

199
00:15:21,730 --> 00:15:26,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one could imagine that she'd be 
a Diva who would save the world.</font>

200
00:15:28,150 --> 00:15:30,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Nagi came back.</font>

201
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:33,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With Kyoya, she was able to.</font>

202
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I won't let Nagi take a lead on me.</font>

203
00:15:38,710 --> 00:15:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll come back to SI-VIS once again.</font>

204
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A large XENOS warship has been detected!</font>

205
00:15:45,980 --> 00:15:47,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell?</font>

206
00:15:47,220 --> 00:15:51,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're devouring asteroids 
around them as they approach.</font>

207
00:15:51,010 --> 00:15:54,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sounds like a black hole.</font>

208
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:57,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And how long until 
Earth is in that range?</font>

209
00:15:57,770 --> 00:16:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their speed goes up each time they 
devour something, so we can't be certain.</font>

210
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'd say one hundred minutes.</font>

211
00:16:05,590 --> 00:16:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And will SI-VIS make it in time?</font>

212
00:16:07,650 --> 00:16:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We received word from Medea-san earlier.</font>

213
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:12,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're not sure either!</font>

214
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:15,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, do calm down!</font>

215
00:16:15,780 --> 00:16:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something similar happened 
ten years ago, you know?</font>

216
00:16:18,540 --> 00:16:22,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you didn't realize it 
until you were attacked, right?</font>

217
00:16:22,180 --> 00:16:24,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we don't need to panic 
before it happens.</font>

218
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that I think about it,</font>

219
00:16:26,910 --> 00:16:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe Harmonia grew this much.</font>

220
00:16:30,050 --> 00:16:32,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did a good job!</font>

221
00:16:32,610 --> 00:16:37,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did such a good job, so I'm 
not going to let it all go to waste.</font>

222
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This must be XENOS's final move.</font>

223
00:16:40,810 --> 00:16:45,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we can get through this 
and defend ourselves, we win!</font>

224
00:16:45,050 --> 00:16:45,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, ma'am!</font>

225
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:54,660
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="13"><font color="#771230">{\an8}This is Nagi's masterpiece!



Write some awesome music for it!</font></font></b></font></font>

226
00:16:47,460 --> 00:16:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unfortunately, you're out of time.</font>

227
00:16:49,860 --> 00:16:54,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">XENOS will... Apollo will soon 
devour all Idea from the Earth.</font>

228
00:16:55,270 --> 00:16:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your song will not save the world.</font>

229
00:16:59,660 --> 00:17:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I wasn't here, that is.</font>

230
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siren, I am going to remove your curse.</font>

231
00:17:06,370 --> 00:17:08,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll turn you back into a normal human.</font>

232
00:17:13,510 --> 00:17:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A normal human isn't going to cut it.</font>

233
00:17:17,430 --> 00:17:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got to be a superstar!</font>

234
00:17:23,270 --> 00:17:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay then. I'll turn you back 
into a superstar.</font>

235
00:17:27,100 --> 00:17:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With my Elpis.</font>

236
00:17:34,950 --> 00:17:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sorry, Lukos.</i></font>

237
00:17:38,370 --> 00:17:44,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not just the people on Earth, 
but my comrades as well.</i></font>

238
00:17:45,390 --> 00:17:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it's okay.</i></font>

239
00:17:48,710 --> 00:17:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I lost you and got caught up in hatred.</i></font>

240
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I took quite a detour, but...</i></font>

241
00:17:57,720 --> 00:18:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>finally, I've arrived.</i></font>

242
00:18:01,990 --> 00:18:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Songs are incredible.</font>

243
00:18:04,260 --> 00:18:06,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They can make people smile.</font>

244
00:18:06,540 --> 00:18:08,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give them power.</font>

245
00:18:08,730 --> 00:18:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And... Songs can even save people.</font>

246
00:18:14,340 --> 00:18:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I want you to save them.</i></font>

247
00:18:16,950 --> 00:18:21,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not just the people on Earth, 
but my comrades as well.</i></font>

248
00:18:23,870 --> 00:18:26,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Goodbye, June...</i></font>

249
00:18:28,730 --> 00:18:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've heard of Elpis.</font>

250
00:18:31,130 --> 00:18:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From your sibling.</font>

251
00:18:33,430 --> 00:18:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I know what you're 
trying to do right now.</font>

252
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I also know that 
it's not the right thing to do.</font>

253
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:44,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me go!</font>

254
00:18:45,780 --> 00:18:48,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Throwing away a life 
in order to save a life.</font>

255
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's something you should never do.</font>

256
00:18:51,690 --> 00:18:53,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the only way!</font>

257
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:57,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To cancel out Lukos's Elpis 
completely, I have to use my Elpis!</font>

258
00:18:58,300 --> 00:19:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doing that will reduce my 
number of fans by one.</font>

259
00:19:03,350 --> 00:19:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am <i>not</i> your fan...</font>

260
00:19:05,080 --> 00:19:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you're a fan of June, 
of SI-VIS. I know it.</font>

261
00:19:23,570 --> 00:19:27,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need to be restored completely.</font>

262
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:30,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just need to be able to sing one song.</font>

263
00:19:31,260 --> 00:19:35,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Five minutes... No, three minutes 
to shine is all I ask.</font>

264
00:19:35,820 --> 00:19:39,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do that without 
sacrificing your life, can't you?</font>

265
00:19:43,070 --> 00:19:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you give it your all?</font>

266
00:19:50,450 --> 00:19:55,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, June's little friend. 
Your name's Krios, right?</font>

267
00:19:55,810 --> 00:19:58,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to embellish my song.</font>

268
00:19:59,290 --> 00:20:02,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want me to...?</font>

269
00:20:02,030 --> 00:20:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi recovered her presence and her Idea</font>

270
00:20:06,660 --> 00:20:10,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">by being with Kyoya and SI-VIS.</font>

271
00:20:11,020 --> 00:20:14,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Nagi can do it, 
there's no reason why I can't.</font>

272
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:16,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's impossible.</font>

273
00:20:16,900 --> 00:20:19,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's the Diva of XENOS.</font>

274
00:20:19,090 --> 00:20:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you're just a normal human—</font>

275
00:20:27,060 --> 00:20:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't I tell you?</font>

276
00:20:28,610 --> 00:20:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a superstar.</font>

277
00:20:31,300 --> 00:20:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who said a superstar 
is inferior to a Diva?</font>

278
00:20:36,990 --> 00:20:38,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to get back.</font>

279
00:20:38,620 --> 00:20:41,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To SI-VIS, to my friends.</font>

280
00:20:41,970 --> 00:20:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And to Kyoya.</font>

281
00:20:52,270 --> 00:20:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't going anywhere.</font>

282
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The whole population 
of Earth could disappear.</font>

283
00:20:58,050 --> 00:21:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you so hung up on this?</font>

284
00:21:01,790 --> 00:21:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A live concert is out of the question.</font>

285
00:21:03,990 --> 00:21:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, you're not even capable of 
the performance of an average person.</font>

286
00:21:08,980 --> 00:21:10,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll work out somehow.</font>

287
00:21:10,860 --> 00:21:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'll make it work.</font>

288
00:21:13,940 --> 00:21:17,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">SI-VIS isn't here. 
Not even Kyoya-kun.</font>

289
00:21:17,390 --> 00:21:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In your condition, there's no way 
your solo can stop XENOS and the Mirage—</font>

290
00:21:21,340 --> 00:21:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I sing, he will come.</font>

291
00:21:25,100 --> 00:21:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So all I have to do is to deliver my song.</font>

292
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To everyone on Earth 
and in the universe.</font>

293
00:22:11,810 --> 00:22:16,940
<font size="20">{\an9}<font size="14"><b><font color="#7279e2">Translator:
Timer:
Editor:
Quality Control:
Final Quality Control:</font></b></font></font>

294
00:22:11,810 --> 00:22:16,940
<font size="20">{\an7}<font size="14"><b><font color="#7279e2">Tomoko Takedani Sater
Krzysztof Kunc
Salem Alabanza
Gabriella Alabanza
Michelle Tymon</font></b></font></font>

295
00:22:27,780 --> 00:22:31,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}On the musical stave
 / In the musical stave</i></font>

296
00:22:31,280 --> 00:22:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}WOW, I let my feelings play
 / I hid my feelings</i></font>

297
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:36,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}My bright future / My pitiful past</i></font>

298
00:22:36,690 --> 00:22:39,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}WOW, started to shine</i></font>

299
00:22:39,160 --> 00:22:41,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Unparalleled / Challenges ahead but</i></font>

300
00:22:41,940 --> 00:22:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}With a smile on my face
 / I'll embrace them</i></font>

301
00:22:44,540 --> 00:22:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I feel like I can even change 
the world with you</i></font>

302
00:22:49,860 --> 00:22:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}(3, 2, 1, Singing over)</i></font>

303
00:22:52,520 --> 00:22:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Intertwining harmony (Harmony)</i></font>

304
00:22:57,580 --> 00:23:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I wouldn't have believed in miracles alone</i></font>

305
00:23:03,590 --> 00:23:08,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}This breathless heartbeat (Heart Beat)</i></font>

306
00:23:08,410 --> 00:23:13,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'll let it resonate in
 the night sky with my voice</i></font>

307
00:23:13,660 --> 00:23:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}My... our dream at full blast</i></font>

308
00:23:25,280 --> 00:23:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Singing over, forever</i></font>

309
00:23:28,180 --> 00:23:31,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Lan lan la la la</i></font>

